		<h2 class="entry-meta">
		by <a href="http://davidstockmanscontracorner.com/author/zerohedge/" title="Posts by ZeroHedge" rel="author">ZeroHedge</a>&nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;<time class="published updated" datetime="2015-01-09">January 9, 2015</time>	</h2>
	</header>
	    <div class="entry-content">
		    <div class="excerpt"><p> The Fed &#8220;is in total denial,&#8221; Roach rants, adding that it &#8220;hasn&#8217;t learned the lessons of what it put the world through a decade ago.&#8221;
<p class="more-link-p"><a class="more-link" href="http://davidstockmanscontracorner.com/stephen-roach-nails-it-again-fed-is-in-total-denial-replicating-same-deadly-trap-as-last-time/">Read on→</a></p>
