	    	</article><!-- #post-36419 -->	<article id="post-34046" class="post-34046 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-david-stockmans-videos-and-podcasts category-stockmans-best-of-the-week category-stockmans-corner c12">
	    <header>
		<h3 class="post-category"><i class="icon-file"></i><a href="http://davidstockmanscontracorner.com/category/stockmans-corner/david-stockmans-videos-and-podcasts/" rel="category tag">Audio and Video</a>, <a href="http://davidstockmanscontracorner.com/category/stockmans-corner/stockmans-best-of-the-week/" rel="category tag">Stockman's Best of the Week</a>, <a href="http://davidstockmanscontracorner.com/category/stockmans-corner/" rel="category tag">Stockman's Corner</a></h3>
